commenter.name: silo_simon
commenter.bio: Hi I'm Sam, when I am streaming, I usually am trying to 100% some games on wii or just doing some language practice on duolingo. I used to stream a lot of speedruns and I still occasionally do speedruns when I am not really busy with school or personal study. I have done two runs at sgdq 2019

message.body: @Silo_Simon Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (266 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case sensitive:

message.body: @mooshal_ytm Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (266 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case sensitive:

message.body: @happybluebird Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (266 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case sensitive:

message.body: @Bit125_ Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (266 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case sensitive: Typing
